            Certified TELUS&nbsp;Health partner agency. Global employee wellbeing plans for organisations that operate across borders.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-[12px] text-[var(--color-ink-mute)]">
            Headquartered in Athens, Greece. Serving brokers, consultancies, and enterprises globally.
